@moresandeep 
If you omit the `hadoop-jwt` completely you can still bypass the authentication, I thought that was the goal to bypass the autnetication. However if your token expires you'll be redirected to the login page when accessing an unauthenticated path, such as /favicon.

In other filters such as `HadoopAuthFilter` we check the unauthenticated path first and do an early return if the path is there.

